---
import Star from '@lucide/astro/icons/star';
import Quote from '@lucide/astro/icons/quote';
import { site } from '../config/site';
---
<section class="bg-muted py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-4xl">
        What Our Clients Say
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        Real results for real people. Read what our clients have to say about their experience working with us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm">
        <Quote class="absolute -top-4 right-4 h-16 w-16 text-primary/10" />
        <div class="mb-4 flex gap-0.5">
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="relative z-10 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          "When I was facing serious charges, Mr. Anderson's expertise and dedication made all the difference. 
          He fought tirelessly for me and secured an outcome I never thought possible. I can't thank him enough."
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">James R.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Criminal Defense Client</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm">
        <Quote class="absolute -top-4 right-4 h-16 w-16 text-primary/10" />
        <div class="mb-4 flex gap-0.5">
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="relative z-10 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          "I was terrified after my DUI arrest, but the team at {site.firmName} walked me through everything step by step. 
          They got my charges significantly reduced and helped me keep my license. Highly recommend."
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Sarah M.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">DUI Defense Client</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm">
        <Quote class="absolute -top-4 right-4 h-16 w-16 text-primary/10" />
        <div class="mb-4 flex gap-0.5">
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
          <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-primary text-primary" />
        </div>
        <p class="relative z-10 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          "After our car accident, we didn't know where to turn. {site.firmName} handled everything with the insurance companies 
          and got us fair compensation. They truly cared about our recovery."
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Robert &amp; Linda T.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Personal Injury Clients</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

